.TH "HPC\-COMPOSE" "1" "" "hpc\-compose 0.1.53" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hpc\-compose \- Compile a compose\-like spec into a single Slurm job
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
hpc\-compose [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Compile a compose\-like specification into one Slurm batch job that launches one or more services through Pyxis/Enroot, Apptainer, Singularity, or host runtime software inside a single allocation. Use plan for static authoring, up for the normal run, and debug for one\-command triage.
